-----------------------
***dm_industrial***
!!! BETA RELEASE !!!
created by warhawk3407
-----------------------

After a couple of weeks, and many hours of work, I just finished the beta release, after a "bad" alpha. I hope this one will be a lot better.

Map inspired by the game play of the very famous "aim_ag_texture2", I turned all the map into something "realistic". I've added the snow and many details.

Have fun guys !

-----------------------

Features :
-24 players support
-Optimisation
-Basic mesh navigation
-NAV file included

-----------------------
